CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 20, 1938, pg. 8, reads: "Smoketown's Frog Week Ends Pleasantly... on the deck at the boatride and Mr. and Mrs. Henry Payne."Cutline of image published in Flash Newspicture Magazine, September 6, 1938, pg. 22, reads: "Says Mr. and Mrs. Henry Payne on board the S. S. St. Paul."
TitMainTitle: Henry Payne and Mrs. Payne posed on deck of Steamer St. Paul, for FROGS week boat ride
